v1.1alpha:

- Increased the number of Tox nodes and added the ability to add user nodes in .json format.
- Increased the response time of the chat area when you open the keyboard.
- Fixed a bug when the application freezes when it's opened from the background.
- Fixed a bug with missing line breaks after quotes in messages.
- Fixed a bug that prevented editing text in the chat area by sending text cursor to the end of line.
- Added confirmation dialog when deleting a friend from the contact list.
- Added the ability to delete chat history for contacts.
- Added the ability to enable or disable saving chat to history.
- Added the ability to change noSpam value (toxcore).